snippet.title: RC Rush - Xbox One Gameplay
snippet.description:
RC Rush is an exciting arcade racing game featuring radio controlled trucks. Win races to unlock career events, compete in head to head battles to unlock new vehicles, and level up your way to becoming the ultimate RC champion!

You'll visit the scrapyards, playgrounds, a volcano and more! You'll compete in places you wouldn't normally be allowed to race RC vehicles, like the inside of an Egyptian tomb!

RC Rush (C) Tea Monster Games
Also available on Steam
